summary: GlobalBank Inc. reported record Q1 earnings of $150M, surpassing expectations due to digital services growth and Fintech Solutions acquisition, increasing market share by 5%.
TechInnovate Solutions recorded $80M Q3 revenues, meeting forecasts, but faces cloud computing competition. A new cybersecurity partnership with SecureNet was formed.
GreenEnergy Corp.'s Q2 profits fell to $20M, a 25% YoY drop, attributed to higher raw material costs and delayed government approvals. Recovery is expected in H2.
